	<itemBody>

		<p>Listen while two friends, Bruno and Valentina, talk about what they like to eat. Then read the sentences below and decide whether each sentence is true (<i>cierto</i>) or false (<i>falso</i>) based on what you hear.</p>

		<audio id="audioElement" controls="controls">
                <source src="audio/unit2_ac1_q1_1.mp3" type="audio/mpeg" />
                </audio>

		<div class="prompt">
				
			<p><audio id="audioElement" controls="controls">
                <source src="audio/1_Bruno.mp3" type="audio/mpeg" />
                </audio></p>
			<p><audio id="audioElement" controls="controls">
                <source src="audio/1_Valentina.mp3" type="audio/mpeg" />
                </audio></p>
			<p><audio id="audioElement" controls="controls">
